{
  "stem": "5758.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But well, apart from this, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the life in Vienna was quite pleasant.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went once a year always on holidays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went to Hungary on Lake Balaton, I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went to Semmering, which is in the mountains, and-- and-- and-- but always only once a year for four weeks, never more than-- than that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, only.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember ever having had a Christian friend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or I don't remember that my parents had Christian friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whenever we went to people's houses, they were always Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I presume it was that hurt feeling, [? had, ?] you know, when-- to protect oneself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One just didn't, because the country itself was terribly antisemitic, very antisemitic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, all the time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the time and very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was the reason, probably, the reason why we didn't have any Christian friends.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know my father had a seat in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He rarely went to synagogue during the years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But on the high holidays, Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur, he went to the synagogue, and we went with him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He-- we had to stand next to him in his-- in his seat and had to pray with him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, we-- we had a Jewish education through learning in-- in that school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The school in gymnasium was split up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Christians had their own religious teaching, and the Jews had their own teaching.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we learned Hebrew, to read Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and I don't think that we learned it to understand it or to-- to-- to-- but to read, yes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We did read.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we had a bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a bar mitzvah at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were only our relatives there, the brother of my mother, and was the family Bodek.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
